The paper also uses the concept of treewidth, which is a well-studied parameter in the field of algorithms and data structures (cs.DS) and logic and verification (cs.LO). Additionally, the paper discusses backdoors, which is a concept used in parameterized complexity (cs.CC) and computational complexity theory (cs.DM).
